==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Centre seal
<hw>Cen"tre seal</hw>,}</mhw>.
<fld>(Gas Manuf.)</fld> <def>A compound hydraulic valve for regulating
the passage of the gas through a set of purifiers so as to cut out each
one in turn for the renewal of the lime.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

